<h4>Anycubic Filament Runout <small>{{ _('Version') }} {{ plugin_anycubicfilamentrunout_plugin_version }}</small></h4>

<p><strong>{{ _('Detection Message:') }}</strong></p>
<p>
{{ _('This plugin monitors the serial communication for a specific message that indicates filament runout.') }}
</p>
<p>
{{ _('The default detection message for Anycubic printers is:') }} <code>echo:Insert filament and send M108</code>
</p>
<p>
{{ _('If your printer uses a different message, you can check the Terminal tab in OctoPrint when a filament runout occurs and update the detection message below.') }}
</p>

<form class="form-horizontal" id="settings_plugin_anycubicfilamentrunout_form">
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Detection Message') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.anycubicfilamentrunout.detection_message">
            <span class="help-block">{{ _('The exact text that appears in the serial output when filament runs out') }}</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</form>
